   <p> <a href="../../K-nightNews.asp">K-night新闻</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;/&nbsp;20150508第八期整车分析谢添嗣</p>
      <hr style="width:860px; margin:6px 0 0 22px;"/>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="article">
<h1 class="MsoNormal" align="center">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span style="font-size:32px;font-family:SimHei;">“</span><span style="font-size:32px;font-family:SimHei;">元老</span><span style="font-size:32px;font-family:SimHei;">”</span><span style="font-size:32px;font-family:SimHei;">修炼手册</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</h1>
<br/>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谢添嗣，<span>2012</span><span>级车辆专业，</span><span>2015</span><span>赛季车队副队长，整车分析组负责人，</span><span>2013</span><span>年加入车队，见证了两辆赛车的诞生！</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>第一章&nbsp;欲练此功，必先</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>……</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>自熏</strong></span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 我可以说是在修车厂长大的，从小耳濡目染的就是</span><span style="font-size:16px;">“</span><span style="font-size:16px;">机油</span><span style="font-size:16px;">…</span><span style="font-size:16px;">扳手</span><span style="font-size:16px;">…”</span><span style="font-size:16px;">。五年级的时候被《速度与激情》系列电影吸引，开始对赛车感兴趣，后来高考结束特意选报了车辆专业。</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>第二章&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>“</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>启</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>”</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>经</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>“</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>拔</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>”</strong></span><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>脉，痛痒难耐</strong></span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 首先是要经常熬夜（所以说车队的人最爱烟熏妆了</span><span style="font-size:16px;">……</span><span style="font-size:16px;">），然后就是赛前比较忙的一段时间会顾不上学业，很紧张。最后就是技术方面，一开始什么都不懂，不知从何做起，基本上是学长让干什么就干什么。平时更多的是花时间自己捉摸钻研。</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center">
	<span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>第三章&nbsp;化境入微，融会贯通</strong></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 我在</span><span style="font-size:16px;">2012</span><span style="font-size:16px;">年</span><span style="font-size:16px;">11</span><span style="font-size:16px;">月份买了《赛车梦》这本书，当时还没有加入车队，读了一遍，后来加入车队，工作学习，参加比赛，又读了一遍，前后的感觉很不一样。亲身经历过，看到书里面的一切，就会感同身受，虽然是写别人的故事，但却像看到了自己，同步的喜怒哀乐。</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center">
	<span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>第四章&nbsp;神功小成，耳聪目明</strong></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 技能方面，相对较早地掌握了入门的三维制图和运动学分析等技术，能够运用所学去参加相关的比赛（大二上学期和同学组队参加了一个汽车造型比赛）；个人综合能力有所提高，做事能力明显提升，性格上，更加外向，也更加自信；还有就是结识了很多朋友，包括学院里面的，也有</span><span style="font-size:16px;">FSC</span><span style="font-size:16px;">圈子里其他高校的。</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center">
	<span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong>第五章&nbsp;功成在即，励世箴言</strong></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 希望每一届的车队都能比前一届做的更好！</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span> 
</p>
